33
00:03:01,959 --> 00:03:03,500
[THUGS]
Huh?

34
00:03:08,542 --> 00:03:11,250
Tch.

35
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:13,500
[GION sighs]

36
00:03:13,583 --> 00:03:16,208
[THUGS laugh]

37
00:03:16,291 --> 00:03:18,667
