59
00:04:16,041 --> 00:04:18,583
[GION]
Enough, man! Put me down!

60
00:04:18,667 --> 00:04:22,583
Hello? What's your
problem, are you deaf?

61
00:04:22,667 --> 00:04:24,333
Put me down!

62
