68
00:04:42,792 --> 00:04:44,125
So thank you.

69
00:04:45,291 --> 00:04:46,667
You're pathetic, dude.

70
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,291
Hey, that's not cool, man.

71
00:04:48,375 --> 00:04:50,792
